Vehicle Mounted Weather Monitoring Station
sponsored by ‘Indian Institute of Remote Sensing & GIS, Nashik’ as a “Research Assistant” under student quality Improvement Program (S-QIP) .

Components Required:
•	Arduino Uno
•	DHT11 (Temperature and Humidity Sensor)
•	BMP180 (Pressure and Temperature Sensor)
•	MQ-2 (Gas Sensor)
•	LCD 16x2
•	ESP8266 (WiFi Module)
•	BLYNK App (for mobile notifications)



